Titolo: Crackdown 2

Anno: 2010

Descrizione: Crackdown 2 is an open world action-adventure video game developed by Ruffian Games and published by Microsoft Game Studios. It was released on Xbox 360 in July 2010 and is a direct sequel to the 2007 video game Crackdown. A sequel, Crackdown 3, was released for the Xbox One and Microsoft Windows in February 2019.

Genere: Action-adventure 

Valutazione: 76
